# Env files in the dotfiles tree are SHAPE-ONLY references with CHANGEME-* placeholders.
# chezmoi must NOT overwrite the live env files on the box, which carry real
# secrets populated by `vault-fetch` (see home/dot_local/bin/executable_vault-fetch)
# at deploy time. Live files live at:
#   - ~/.config/sodimo/<service>.env
#   - ~/.config/containers/systemd/<service>.env (legacy path; being migrated)
# Both are mode 0600 and source-of-truth for whatever is actually running.
